message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and coding. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as the paper deals with the transmission of data, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper deals with the distortion of data, cs.SI (social and information networks) as the paper deals with the transmission of information, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with the distortion of multimedia data.
